OL,3,CAre we heading for a new PM - and is
OL,4,Cnow the time for a leadership contest?
OL,6,FPolitical Correspondent Tom Sheldrick
OL,7,Fis joined by Sam Rushworth MP
OL,8,F(Labour), Baroness McIntosh of
OL,9,FPickering (Con), and Lord Purvis of
OL,10,FTweed (Lib Dem) on Thursday 14 May 2026
OL,12,FReform UK's victories across the north
OL,13,Fof England have piled pressure on the
OL,14,FPrime Minister, with Labour divided
OL,15,Fover whether it's the right time for a
OL,16,Fleadership contest - and who should be
OL,17,Fin the running.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/3
